ettus_leschenaultii_Harvard.jpg/220px-Rousettus_leschenaultii_Harvard.jpg',NULL),(3999,'马达加斯加果蝠/马岛果蝠','Rousettus madagascariensis',1172,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4000,'科摩罗果蝠','Rousettus obliviosus',1172,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4001,'棘果蝠/光背果蝠','Rousettus spinalatus',1172,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4002,'蜥齿灰果蝠/蛇齿夜果蝠','Scotonycteris ophiodon',1173,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4003,'灰果蝠/詹氏夜果蝠','Scotonycteris zenkeri',1173,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4004,'布氏球果蝠/短球鼻果蝠','Sphaerias blanfordi',1174,'布氏球果蝠（学名：Sphaerias blanfordi）为狐蝠科球果蝠属的动物。在中国大陆，分布于西藏等地。[2]','布氏球果蝠（学名：Sphaerias blanfordi）为狐蝠科球果蝠属的动物。在中国大陆，分布于西藏等地。[2]0',1,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24','//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Bush_dog.JPG/220px-Bush_dog.JPG',NULL),(4005,'花面狐蝠/纹面狐蝠','Styloctenium wallacei',1175,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4006,'捷果蝠/短鼻快翼果蝠','Thoopterus nigrescens',1176,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4007,'小鼠尾蝠','Rhinopoma hardwickii',1177,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4008,'大鼠尾蝠','Rhinopoma microphyllum',1177,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4009,'鼠尾蝠/阿曼鼠尾蝠','Rhinopoma muscatellum',1177,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4010,'非洲假吸血蝠/心鼻蝠','Cardioderma cor',1178,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,NULL),(4011,'黄翼蝠/黄翼洗浣蝠','Lavia frons',1179,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2023-06-08 16:45:23','2023-06-08 16:45:24',NULL,'https://media.gettyimages.com/id/81989345/zh/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87/kisoro-district-near-lake-mutanda-western-uganda.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=3LjyZeatOmqiQUFIAyfMUYLMe8C8Of5cis1pOCqmQvM='),(4012,'澳洲假吸血蝠','Macroderma gigas',1180,NULL,NULL,0,0,'202